# Phase 5: QA & Validation Testing Guide

## Manual Testing - Happy Paths

### Path 1: Landing → Pricing → Register → Onboarding → Dashboard → Logout
- [ ] Navigate to Landing Page (/)
- [ ] Verify landing page loads without errors
- [ ] Click "Pricing" button/nav
- [ ] Verify pricing page loads correctly
- [ ] Click "Sign Up" or similar registration CTA
- [ ] Navigate to registration form
- [ ] Fill out registration form with valid data
- [ ] Submit registration
- [ ] Verify onboarding flow starts
- [ ] Complete onboarding steps
- [ ] Navigate to dashboard
- [ ] Verify dashboard loads correctly
- [ ] Test logout functionality
- [ ] Verify redirect to landing page

### Path 2: Landing → Login → Dashboard → Settings → Logout
- [ ] Navigate to Landing Page (/)
- [ ] Click "Sign In" button
- [ ] Navigate to login form
- [ ] Fill out login form with valid credentials
- [ ] Submit login
- [ ] Verify redirect to dashboard
- [ ] Navigate to settings page
- [ ] Verify settings page loads correctly
- [ ] Test logout functionality
- [ ] Verify redirect to landing page

### Path 3: Landing → Pricing → Register (paid) → Onboarding → Checkout → Dashboard
- [ ] Navigate to Landing Page (/)
- [ ] Click "Pricing" button
- [ ] Verify pricing page displays subscription tiers
- [ ] Select a paid subscription plan
- [ ] Navigate to registration
- [ ] Complete registration with billing info
- [ ] Complete onboarding flow
- [ ] Navigate to checkout/payment
- [ ] Verify payment processing
- [ ] Navigate to dashboard
- [ ] Verify premium features are accessible

### Path 4: Dashboard → Try access Premium feature → Locked → Pricing → Checkout
- [ ] Login as free user
- [ ] Navigate to dashboard
- [ ] Try to access premium feature (Portfolio, Advanced Signals, etc.)
- [ ] Verify feature is locked with upgrade prompt
- [ ] Click upgrade/pricing CTA
- [ ] Navigate to pricing page
- [ ] Select premium plan
- [ ] Navigate to checkout
- [ ] Complete payment
- [ ] Verify premium access granted

### Path 5: Mobile versions of all above
- [ ] Test Path 1 on mobile viewport
- [ ] Test Path 2 on mobile viewport  
- [ ] Test Path 3 on mobile viewport
- [ ] Test Path 4 on mobile viewport
- [ ] Verify mobile navigation works
- [ ] Verify mobile responsive design
- [ ] Test touch interactions

## Manual Testing - Error Cases

### Authentication Errors
- [ ] Login with wrong password
- [ ] Login with non-existent email
- [ ] Register with existing email
- [ ] Register with invalid email format
- [ ] Register with weak password

### Route Protection
- [ ] Access protected route (/app/*) without login
- [ ] Access onboarding route when completed
- [ ] Access expired session routes
- [ ] Direct URL manipulation

### Network & Session
- [ ] Network error during login
- [ ] Token expiry mid-session
- [ ] Browser back/forward edge cases
- [ ] Page refresh during critical flows

### Payment & Checkout
- [ ] Payment failure flow
- [ ] Invalid payment details
- [ ] Payment timeout scenarios
- [ ] Checkout cancellation

## Performance & Accessibility

### Performance Metrics
- [ ] Page load times < 3 seconds
- [ ] Lighthouse score > 85
- [ ] No console errors/warnings
- [ ] No memory leaks (basic check)

### Accessibility Audit
- [ ] Keyboard navigation (Tab, Enter, Esc)
- [ ] Screen reader compatibility
- [ ] Color contrast (WCAG AA minimum)
- [ ] Focus indicators visible
- [ ] Forms have proper labels
- [ ] ARIA attributes where needed

### Security Review
- [ ] XSS prevention (input sanitization)
- [ ] CSRF protection
- [ ] Secure token storage
- [ ] HTTPS enforcement
- [ ] CSP headers validation

## Cross-browser Testing
- [ ] Chrome (desktop & mobile)
- [ ] Safari (desktop & mobile iOS)
- [ ] Firefox
- [ ] Edge

## Success Criteria
- ✅ No P0/P1 bugs
- ✅ Lighthouse score > 85
- ✅ Works on major browsers & devices
- ✅ All happy paths complete successfully
- ✅ Error cases handled gracefully